#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:188
msgid ""
"Upon clicking :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`, Odoo reveals the "
":guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft`, *only* showing that reached milestone in"
